Class SolicitaSvc

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.svc.AbstractSvc<P,Q>
com.sicomsa.dmt.svc.AbstractGenericSvc<SolicitaResponse,Query>
com.sicomsa.dmt.svc.SolicitaSvc
All Implemented Interfaces:
Service<SolicitaResponse,Query>
public class SolicitaSvc extends AbstractGenericSvc<SolicitaResponse,Query>
Extends AbstractGenericSvc to provide a concrete implementation of the WS defined for requesting downloads:
"https://cfdidescargamasivasolicitud.clouda.sat.gob.mx/SolicitaDescargaService.svc"

This class has concrete methods to add content of the download request (Query) to the SOAPMessage to send, sign the message, and parse the response from SAT in a SolicitaResponse instance which will contain the relevant data of the response.

If SolicitaResponse's method isAccept(), returns true will mean the request was accepted and we can now verify using SolicitaResponse's method getRequestId() which will give us the request id that should be used to verify the request.
